-cid-yfkj2dxk>Persons</span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n        </ul><ul class=\"g-nav__list\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n          <li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/work-style\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>働く環境を知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Work Style</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/numbers\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>数字から知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Numbers</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/recruit\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>採用について</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Recruit</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/faq\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>よくある質問</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>FAQ</span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n        </ul>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n    <div class=\"header-nav__link\" data-astro-cid-ytipa35t>\n      <a class=\"instagram\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mutoh_recruit/\" target=\"_blank\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>\n  <img class=\"instagram__icon\" src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/Instagram_Glyph_Black.svg\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>\n  <p class=\"instagram__text\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>ムトウ採用担当<br data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>公式Instagram</p>\n</a>\n      <a class=\"external-button external-button--transparent\" href=\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>\n  <p class=\"external-button__text\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>Corporate Site</p>\n  <img class=\"external-button__icon\" src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/external-icon.svg\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>\n</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  \n</header>\n    <main>\n      <div class=\"l-breadcrumbs\">\n                <div class=\"main-inner\">\n                  <astro-breadcrumbs data-main-bem-class=\"c-breadcrumbs\" data-id=\"ea21102a-f61a-4259-b74e-137b5c5fbdd5\" data-path-length=\"2\">\n  <nav aria-label=\"breadcrumbs\" class=\"c-breadcrumbs\" id=\"ea21102a-f61a-4259-b74e-137b5c5fbdd5\">\n    <ol class=\"c-breadcrumbs__crumbs has-no-separators\">\n      <li class=\"c-breadcrumbs__crumb\">\n              \n\n              <a href=\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/\" class=\"c-breadcrumbs__link\">\n                  TOP\n                </a>\n\n              \n            </li>\n          <li class=\"c-breadcrumbs__crumb\">\n              \n\n              <a href=\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/work-style/\" class=\"c-breadcrumbs__link is-current\" aria-current=\"location\">\n                  働く環境を知る\n                </a>\n\n              \n            </li>\n          \n    </ol>\n  </nav>\n</astro-breadcrumbs>\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"item\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/\",\"name\":\"TOP\"}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"item\":{\"@id\":\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/work-style/\",\"name\":\"働く環境を知る\"}}]}</script>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n      \n  <div id=\"js-intro\" class=\"intro\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n  <div class=\"intro__wrap\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n    <div class=\"intro__inner\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n      <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n        <h1 class=\"intro__heading\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n          <span class=\"intro__lead\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>Work Style</span>\n          <b class=\"intro__title\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>働く環境を<wbr>知る</b>\n        </h1>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <figure class=\"intro__img\" data-astro-cid-hxrq4k5a>\n      <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/work-style_intro.jpg\" width=\"670\" height=\"432\" alt=\"\">\n  </figure>\n  </div>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"main-container\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>\n    <aside class=\"main-container__aside\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>\n      <nav class=\"main-container__nav side-nav\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>\n        <ul class=\"side-nav__list\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>\n          <li class=\"side-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns><a href=\"#career-advance\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>キャリアアップ</a></li><li class=\"side-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns><a href=\"#training\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>研修制度</a></li><li class=\"side-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns><a href=\"#job-rotation\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>ジョブローテーション制度</a></li><li class=\"side-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns><a href=\"#benefits\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>福利厚生</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </nav>\n    </aside>\n    <div class=\"main-container__body\" data-astro-cid-hd2plnns>\n      \n    <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n      <section id=\"career-advance\" class=\"work-style\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n        <div class=\"main-wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n          <h2 class=\"heading2\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>\n  <b class=\"heading2__lead\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>Career Advance</b>\n  <span class=\"heading2__title\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>キャリアアップ</span>\n</h2>\n          <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>現場でキャリアを積むだけではなく、各種研修や転勤などを通じ経験を重ねることでスキルアップし、ムトウグループを率いる存在へと成長することができます。</p>\n          <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <div class=\"work-style__img\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <figure data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/career-advance01.svg\" alt=\"新入社員は「新人研修」、「OJT研修」、「フォロー研修」、\n                入社8年から14年目で係長・副課長として「初級管理職研修」を、\n                入社15年から20年目で支店長・課長として「新任店所長ガイダンス」、「中間管理職研修」を、\n                入社20年以上になると上級管理職（部長・本部長）として「上級管理職研修」を行います。\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              </figure>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <section id=\"training\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n      <div class=\"main-wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n          <h2 class=\"heading2\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>\n  <b class=\"heading2__lead\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>Training</b>\n  <span class=\"heading2__title\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>研修制度</span>\n</h2>\n          <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>社内に人事部研修所という部署を設け、社員の経験・能力に応じて各種研修を実施し、社員の成長をバックアップする仕組みを構築しています。</p>\n          <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <div class=\"tab__wrap\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n  <ul class=\"tab__list\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n    <li class=\"tab__list-item\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <button class=\"tab__button js-tab\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">新入社員導入研修</button>\n        </li><li class=\"tab__list-item\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <button class=\"tab__button js-tab\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">OJT研修</button>\n        </li><li class=\"tab__list-item\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <button class=\"tab__button js-tab\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">フォロー研修</button>\n        </li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <div class=\"tab__panel\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n    <div class=\"tab__body js-tabs__body\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <div class=\"tab-content__unit\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                <figure data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                      <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/training-tab01.png\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                    </figure>\n                    <p class=\"tab-content__text\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">入社から3日間は札幌本社で集合研修を行います。<br>挨拶や名刺交換、電話応対など基礎的なビジネスマナーや社内の仕組み、コンプライアンス等について研修を行います。</p>\n              </div>\n        </div><div class=\"tab__body js-tabs__body\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <div class=\"tab-content__unit\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                <figure data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                      <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/training-tab02.png\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                    </figure>\n                    <p class=\"tab-content__text\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">OJT＝On the Job Trainingの略称です。配属先へ着任後3か月間は、OJT期間として先輩社員との同行を通して仕事を学んでいただきます。</p>\n              </div>\n        </div><div class=\"tab__body js-tabs__body\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n          <div class=\"tab-content__unit\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                <figure data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                      <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/training-tab03.png\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">\n                    </figure>\n                    <p class=\"tab-content__text\" data-astro-cid-ucxf2vnx style=\"--tabLength: 3;\">複数社の主要取引メーカーに協力いただき実施する医療知識習得のための勉強会や実際にサンプルを手に取って行うワークショップ、先輩社員が講師となって行う社内ルールや日常的に使用するシステムの解説、職場メンバーからのアセスメントとディスカッションによる分析と相互検討など、幅広いプログラムに沿って行います。</p>\n              </div>\n        </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <h3 class=\"work-style__title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>その他の研修</h3>\n            <div class=\"work-style__inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <ul class=\"work-style__list\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>メーカー研修</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>月2回程度、新製品や新規取り扱いメーカーの説明会を、社内のWebシステムを利用して開催。</p>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>ムトウグループ学会</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>社内の経営や業務に関する課題について、抜本的な改革を意識し、ムトウグループの社員同士で検討・発表。</p>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>通信教育</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>様々な分野の講座が受講可能。受講費用の半額は会社から補助。</p>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>QCサークル活動</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>自部署が抱えている問題の改善策を検討・実施・発表。</p>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>コンプライアンス研修</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>医療業界での法令順守に対応する必要があるため、定期的に実施。</p>\n                    </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"main-wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n          <div class=\"work-style__box\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <figure data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/career-advance_avatar.png\" width=\"282\" height=\"282\" alt=\"\">\n              </figure>\n            <div class=\"work-style__body\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <h4 class=\"work-style__box-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>研修所所長より</h4>\n              <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>研修を実施する上では、「教える」より「気づき」を促すことやオンライン実施時でも受講者同士交流する時間を大事に心掛けています。受講者目線の分かりやすい言葉で説明し、受講することで理解が深まるようにしているので、安心して入社してくださいね！</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"job-rotation\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n      <div class=\"main-wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n          <h2 class=\"heading2\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>\n  <b class=\"heading2__lead\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>Job Rotation</b>\n  <span class=\"heading2__title\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>ジョブローテーション制度</span>\n</h2>\n          <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>さまざまな経験を積み、広い視野を持った人材を育成するため、ジョブローテーション制度を導入しています。<br data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>ジョブローテーションによる組織の活性化にも期待しています。</p>\n          \n          <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <div class=\"work-style__inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <ul class=\"work-style__list\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>入社時の配属先</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>人事部にて当人の性格や配属先の状況を考慮し決定します。<br>※一部エリアで地域限定採用を行っています。</p>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style__list-item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <h4 class=\"work-style__list-title\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>転勤の頻度</h4>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>平均３～５年ごと</p>\n                    </li>\n              </ul>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"work-style__button\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <a href=\"/recruit_plus/faq/\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>その他の疑問は<wbr data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>「よくある質問」をご確認ください</p>\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"5.061\" height=\"8.707\" viewBox=\"0 0 5.061 8.707\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                  <path d=\"M904.927,1355.577l4,4-4,4\" transform=\"translate(-904.573 -1355.224)\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#0d1e5f\" stroke-width=\"1\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu></path>\n                </svg>     \n              </a>         \n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"benefits\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n      <div class=\"main-wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n        <div class=\"main-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n          <h2 class=\"heading2\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>\n  <b class=\"heading2__lead\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>Benefits</b>\n  <span class=\"heading2__title\" data-astro-cid-ny5euywa>福利厚生</span>\n</h2>\n          <div class=\"work-style__title work-style__title--center\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu><h3 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>健康サポート</h3></div>\n          <div class=\"work-style__benefits work-style-benefits\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n            <ul class=\"work-style-benefits__list\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                    <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>健康手当</h4>\n                    <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>健康促進として禁煙を推奨。喫煙者ではない場合、または禁煙したという方には毎月、健康手当が支給されます。</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li><li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                    <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>医療相談窓口設置</h4>\n                    <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>当社の顧問である先生（医師）へ健康に関する相談が可能な窓口を設置。相談内容も先生と相談者の情報共有のみとし、会社は関与しませんので、安心して相談いただけます。</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li><li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                    <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>健康診断受診</h4>\n                    <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>年に1回、基本的な健診を受けていただきます（オプション健診は個人負担）。</p>\n                    </div>\n                  </li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n              <ul class=\"work-style-benefits__list work-style-benefits__list--img\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__item-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <figure data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                          <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/benefits_img01.jpg\" width=\"502.5\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>長期休暇制度</h4>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>夏期もしくは冬期に連続5日間(平日)の休暇を取得できる制度です。土日を含めると最大9日間の休暇となるので、旅行や趣味に時間を費やしリフレッシュしていただけます！</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__item-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <figure data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                          <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/benefits_img02.jpg\" width=\"502.5\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>確定拠出</h4>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>企業型確定拠出年金（ＤＣ）を活用し従業員の皆様のセカンドライフに備えた資産形成を会社が支援する福利厚生制度です。ＤＣ掛金を拠出するか、前払退職金として給与で受取るかは個人の自由（任意）。ＤＣ掛金額も個人の自由（決められたパターンの中での選択）。</p>\n                        \n                      </div>\n                    </li><li class=\"work-style-benefits__item\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__item-inner\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <figure data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                          <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/benefits_img03.jpg\" width=\"502.5\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\">\n                        </figure>\n                        <h4 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>保養所</h4>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                        <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>全国に6箇所ある施設を、社員価格で安く利用できます。</p>\n                        <div class=\"work-style-benefits__textarea--list\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                              <h5 data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>施設</h5>\n                              <p data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>ニセコ･トマム・軽井沢・箱根・伊勢志摩・南阿蘇 他</p>\n                            </div>\n                      </div>\n                    </li>\n              </ul>\n\n              <div class=\"work-style__wrap\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                <div class=\"work-style__butto work-style__button--dafault\" data-astro-cid-vm7s45cu>\n                  <a class=\"default-button\" href=\"/recruit_plus/recruit/\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>\n  <p class=\"default-button__text\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7>募集要項を見る</p>\n  <div class=\"default-button__arrow\" data-astro-cid-6p6x3ly7></div>\n</a>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  \n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n\n\n\n    </main>\n    <footer data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n  <div class=\"footer\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n    <div class=\"footer__container main-inner\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n      <a class=\"footer__entry\" href=\"https://wismmutoh.snar.jp/entry.aspx?entryid=e54b569a-3f41-45e0-b9ed-d73c907a6d1b\" target=\"_blank\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n        <span data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n          <b data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>ENTRY</b>\n          <p data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>マイページへ</p>\n        </span>\n        <div class=\"footer__entry-arrow\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf></div>\n      </a>\n      <div class=\"footer__inner\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n        <div class=\"footer__link\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n          <a class=\"footer__logo\" href=\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n            <img src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/logo.svg\" alt=\"wism 株式会社ムトウ\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n            <b data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>RECRUIT SITE</b>\n          </a>\n          <a class=\"instagram\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mutoh_recruit/\" target=\"_blank\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>\n  <img class=\"instagram__icon\" src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/Instagram_Glyph_Black.svg\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>\n  <p class=\"instagram__text\" data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>ムトウ採用担当<br data-astro-cid-p3zb73w3>公式Instagram</p>\n</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"footer__nav\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n          <nav class=\"g-nav\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n  <div class=\"g-nav__inner g-nav__inner--footer\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n    <ul class=\"g-nav__list\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n          <li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/about-us\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>会社について知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>About Us</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/business\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>仕事について知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Business</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/persons\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>働く社員の声から知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Persons</span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n        </ul><ul class=\"g-nav__list\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n          <li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/work-style\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>働く環境を知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Work Style</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/numbers\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>数字から知る</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Numbers</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/recruit\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>採用について</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>Recruit</span>\n                </a>\n              </li><li class=\"g-nav__list-item\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                <a href=\"/recruit_plus/faq\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>\n                  <b class=\"g-nav__title\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>よくある質問</b>\n                  <span class=\"g-nav__lead\" data-astro-cid-yfkj2dxk>FAQ</span>\n                </a>\n              </li>\n        </ul>\n  </div>\n</nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"footer__part\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>\n        <a class=\"external-button external-button--transparent\" href=\"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>\n  <p class=\"external-button__text\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>Corporate Site</p>\n  <img class=\"external-button__icon\" src=\"/recruit_plus/assets/images/external-icon.svg\" alt=\"\" data-astro-cid-yua3altl>\n</a>\n        <p class=\"footer__copylight\" data-astro-cid-tnm6jnzf>© Mutoh Group. All Right Reserved.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</footer>\n  </body></html>","finalUrl":"https://www.wism-mutoh.jp/recruit_plus/work-style/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-22T21:06:35.598Z"}